#text=On Arbor Day of 2014 , I planted a tree .
#text=I chose a hardy Colorado Blue Spruce evergreen tree from arborday.org .
#text=This website makes learning about planting trees easy .
#text=I could have chosen to wait to plant my tree because they come in tiny plastic tubes that can be stored in the refrigerator for when I am ready .
#text=The Colorado Blue Spruce grows well in my area of the United States .
#text=I 'm not a tree expert so I wanted a tree that would not need a lot of skill to plant .
#text=It will be many , many years before my tree becomes a tall and magnificent giant but I know I did something good for our Earth by planting it .
#text=I am going to plant a tree every year for Arbor Day because I loved how easy it was .
#text=It has only been a year but my little tree is growing out of the ground and I have n't had to do anything to tend to it .
